/** createBrushAlpha
  */
[RoutineDef, createBrushAlpha
,
	[IFreeze,
	 
		/* LOAD TOOL */ 
		[IPress,Tool:Cube3D]
		[CanvasStroke,(
		)]
		[IPress,Transform: Edit]
		[IPress,Transform:Fit]
		//[IPress,Tool:Make PolyMesh3D]
		
		/* CREATE AlphaBrush */ 
		[IPress,Alpha:Alpha 01]
		[CanvasStroke,(ZObjStrokeV03n2%p5E9FFF8p3E68000PNNN-1s3DA7FFCs3DA7FFCs3DA7FFCZ=
		YH5C4V424K2XH5C4V424)]
		
		/* NEW DOCUMENT */ 
		[IKeyPress, 78,[IPress, Document:New Document]]
		
		/* RESET TOOLS */ 
		[IKeyPress,'1', [IReset, 3]]
		[IPress,Tool:SimpleBrush]
	]

]
